 {"id":"bd-1wv","title":"CLI/Model unit tests + e2e validation","description":"WHAT: Test coverage for all CLI and model changes. (1) Unit tests: exit code verification for --check-drift (mock scenarios returning 0/1/2), BV_PRETTY_JSON env var produces indented output, --related-min-relevance and --related-max-results filter correctly, DateTime<Utc> serialization round-trips through JSON/YAML/TOON, is_closed() vs is_tombstone() return correct booleans for all status values, content_hash computed correctly for known inputs, external_ref stored and retrieved. (2) E2e script (scripts/test_cli_parity.sh) that exercises every changed flag against real fixture data, verifying: exit codes match expectations, env var behavior, flag parsing edge cases (missing value, invalid type, conflicting flags). LOGGING: Each test logs the command invoked, env vars set, expected outcome, actual outcome. On failure, dump stderr and the full CLI help output for context. EDGE CASES: Empty input, Unicode in issue titles, zero-length content_hash input, future timestamps, epoch 0 timestamps. ACCEPTANCE: All flag changes have both positive and negative test cases. E2e script exits 0. PARENT: bd-36l","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:26:17.645662260Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-09T20:21:16.898606237Z","closed_at":"2026-03-09T20:21:16.898191219Z","close_reason":"CLI/model integration tests: 39 tests covering drift exit codes, related-work flag parsing, status semantics, content_hash/external_ref serialization, empty/unicode edge cases, flag parsing errors, self-diff, forecast/capacity/history/graph/metrics output shapes. Fixed tui.rs brace mismatch in History Author search, created missing actionable_detail snapshot. 1014 total tests, 0 failures.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1wv","depends_on_id":"bd-36l.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:19.838648871Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1wv","depends_on_id":"bd-36l.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:20.206992555Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1wv","depends_on_id":"bd-36l.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:20.610518526Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1wv","depends_on_id":"bd-36l.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:21.005143534Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1wv","depends_on_id":"bd-36l.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:21.407209863Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1wv","depends_on_id":"bd-36l.6","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:27:21.791096396Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":48,"issue_id":"bd-1wv","author":"Dicklesworthstone","text":"TESTING STRATEGY: CLI tests are straightforward — assert_cmd crate handles most of the heavy lifting. Key edge cases: what happens when BV_PRETTY_JSON is set to '0' vs 'false' vs ''? What happens when --check-drift finds no beads dir? DateTime parsing of legacy String timestamps — test the migration path specifically. The e2e script should exercise the FULL CLI surface, not just changed flags.","created_at":"2026-03-08T00:28:18Z"}]}
